title: Arbor Skateboards :: 2015 Product Profiles - Genesis
description:
The Genesis is our top line cruiser, a drop-through hour glass shape, with a damp flex and a wider and more functional standing platform. Take advantage of the kicktails for added freestyle versatility.

L: 44.00” W: 9.60” WB: 32.00”
